Package: BigDataPE
Title: Secure and Intuitive Access to 'BigDataPE' 'API' Datasets
Version: 0.0.95
Date: 2025-02-13
Authors@R: c(
            person("Andre", "Leite", email = "leite@castlab.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Hugo", "Vaconcelos", email = "hugo.vasconcelos@ufpe.br", role = "aut"),
            person("Diogo", "Bezerra", email = "diogo.bezerra@ufpe.br", role = "aut"))
Description: Designed to simplify the process of retrieving datasets from the 'BigDataPE' <https://is.gd/SQyA8D> platform using secure token-based authentication. It provides functions for securely storing, retrieving, and managing tokens associated with specific datasets, as well as fetching and processing data using the 'httr2' package. 
